---
title: Smart Turkey Satay Salad with Marinated Radishes and Mango
description: South Asian-inspired flavours take centre stage in this yummy salad. Ground turkey is sautéed with aromatic ginger, then dressed in a nutty soy-peanut vinaigrette. Juicy bursts of pickled radish and mango bring bold bites of freshness. The best part? This recipe works beautifully with both ripe and unripe mangoes!
